Database is used to store the metadata of the tables under it.

Commands related to a database:

1.  create database d1;

2.  create database if not exists d1;

3.  describe database d1;

4.  create database if not exists d2 comment "this is a database";

5.  describe database extended d2;

6.  we can also create a database with dbproperties. There are some 
    predefined dbproperties linked with the database.

    create database if not exists d3 with dbproperties('creator'='rahul', 'date'='2021-11-16');

    describe database extended d3;

7.  List all the databases =  show databases;

8.  If a table is created without mentioning database name and particular database is not checked out, 
    than it will be created under 'default' database.

9.  checkout or use particular database = use d2;
